---
title: Creamy Baked Cheese Pasta with cherry tomatoes and butternut squash
description: Something wonderful happens to Greek style cheese when you bake it at blistering temperatures. It softens and becomes almost creamy, creating the most amazing pasta sauce. Softened cherry tomatoes and sweet roasted butternut squash also benefit from a stint in the searing hot oven.
